33 SECTION 2. IC 5-30-8-8 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA CODE
34 AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE JULY
35 1, 2026]: Sec. 8. (a) The definitions set forth in IC 5-16-13-4 apply
36 throughout this section.
37 (b) This section applies after June 30, 2026, only to a contractor
38 that employs ten (10) or more employees.
39 (c) This section does not apply to a:
40 (1) developer; or
41 (2) general contractor;
42 unless the developer or general contractor has at least one (1)
